# subscript(_:)

**Instance Subscript**

Accesses a slice of the data frame type with an index range.

## Declaration

```swift
subscript(range: Range<Int>) -> DataFrame.Slice { get set }
```

## Parameters

- **range**: An integer range.

## Accessing Rows

- **subscript(_:)**: Accesses rows of a data frame type with an index range expression.
